data.meta_description: Shop Self Tan, Skincare and Suncare online at Bondi Sands - Australian Made, Globally Loved.
data.text:
Australian Made, Globally Loved

More than the best self tanning products, Bondi Sands is about sand, sea and sun and the lifestyle that comes with it. Inspired by Australias most well known beach, and a desire to make the ultimate tan accessible to everyone, our salon quality formulas work to give you an even, naturally golden tan that hydrates and nourishes your skin meaning you stay bronzed for longer.

Owned and made in Australia. Welcome to Bondi Sands - The Australian Tan.
